 Baldwin’s Beware the Cat, Robert Greene’s Pandosto and Menaphon, Philip Sidney’s Old and New Arcadia, and Thomas Lodge’s Rosalynd and A Margarite of America, George Gascoigne’s Steele Glas, John Lyly’s Euphues: An Anatomy of Wit and Euphues and his England, Barnabe Riche’s Farewell, Greene’s A Quip for an Upstart Courtier, and Thomas Nashe’s The Unfortunate Traveller.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aDisguise in literature. 0aEnglish fictionyEarly modern, 1500-1700xHistory and criticism. 0aLord's Supper in literature. 0aReformation in literature. 0aRomances, EnglishxHistory and criticism. 0aTransubstantiation in literature. 4aAbendmahl. 4aBritische Literatur. 4aFrühe Neuzeit/Literatur. 4aProsaliteratur. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / English, Irish, Scottish, Welsh.2bisacsh  aBritish Literature.  aEarly Modern Literature.  aEucharist Debate.  aProse Fiction.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Literary and Cultural Studies 2000-2014 (EN)z978311023846408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Literary and Cultural Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110637854oZDB-23-GLC08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2014z9783110370270oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831103949620 cprintz978311034334240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311034338040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110343380423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110343380/original  a978-3-11-023846-4  DGBA Backlist Literary and Cultural Studies 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete 